Class NumberTag

java.lang.Object
org.moddingx.launcherlib.nbt.tag.NumberTag
All Implemented Interfaces:
Tag
public final class NumberTag extends Object implements Tag
A numeric tag. Covers tag types TagType.BYTE, TagType.SHORT, TagType.INT, TagType.LONG, TagType.FLOAT and TagType.DOUBLE.
